	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"after finally finding a working rom for this game, I started to tas it.  I didn’t expect to find some neat glitches with it (though I should have, considering it’s a bootleg)
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	(youtube|v=At3Rv8CexM8)
	$LF
]div
